description: Welcome to "The mental world of a visual artist from the Middle East(TMOV) Visoal art project. Each piece Of this collection has a unique idea that contains a message or a feeling for the people of the world. TMOV Project seeks to create a new visual language for communication between people of all races of the world.  Part of the project revenue will be spent on combating racism NGOs .So become a member of the big TMOV family by buying nfts from this collection. Limited Versions: 2021
